tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE demand_forecast_data (
   id UUID NOT NULL,
   partner_id UUID NOT NULL,
   forecast_date DATE NOT NULL,
   demand_quantity INT NOT NULL,
   PRIMARY KEY (id)
);

CREATE TABLE inventory_planning (
   id UUID NOT NULL,
   partner_id UUID NOT NULL,
   product_id UUID NOT NULL,
   planned_quantity INT NOT NULL,
   planning_date DATE NOT NULL,
   PRIMARY KEY (id)
);

CREATE TABLE demand_forecast (
 forecast_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 partner_id INT,
 forecast_date DATE,
 forecast_qty INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES partners(partner_id)
);

CREATE TABLE partners (
    partner_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name STRING,
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    contact_person STRING,
    contact_email STRING
)

CREATE TABLE demand_forecast (
    forecast_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_id UUID,
    forecast_date DATE,
    forecast_qty INTEGER,
    CONSTRAINT fk_partner_id FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES partners(partner_id)
)

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    inventory_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name STRING,
    product_sku STRING,
    in_stock_qty INTEGER,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_id UUID,
    collaboration_start_date DATE,
    collaboration_type STRING,
    CONSTRAINT fk_collab_partner_id FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES partners(partner_id)
)

CREATE TABLE inventory_planning (
  inventory_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  location_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE demand_forecast_approval (
  approval_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  forecast_id INT,
  approver_id INT,
  approval_status VARCHAR(20),
  approval_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaboration_logs (
  log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  action VARCHAR(50),
  action_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  user_id INT,
  details TEXT
);
